      public void makeNewAccount(String username, long score)
      Method Adds user's username and score into the ArrayList accounts
      Parameters:
      username - Scenario 1: If txt file is empty Variable passed from EndGame -> user inputs into textfield and is captured and then set into this.username. Scenario 2: If txt file is not empty Variable passed from st1 -> Scanner that detects the username from a specific txt file, for example: 4-AccountList.txt
      score - Scenario 1: If txt file is empty Variable passed from EndGame -> user inputs into textfield and is captured and then set into this.username. Scenario 2: If txt file is not empty Variable passed from st2-> Scanner that detects the score from a specific txt file, for example: 4-AccountList.txt
